Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.87,0:01:49.68,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}仿佛身处幸福的桃源
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.32,0:01:55.19,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}分享秘密的他
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.47,0:01:59.05,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}却爬在我头上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.34,0:02:01.36,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}告诉那家伙
